# packetFlow

**Instance Property**

A [doc://com.apple.networkextension/documentation/NetworkExtension/NEPacketTunnelFlow] object which is used to receive IP packets routed to the tunnel’s virtual interface and inject IP packets into the networking stack via the tunnel’s virtual interface.
